  "2026-06-30T22:01:43.992Z",claude-code-agent,"Progress evidence: broadened CodeFactor complexity cleanup now removes 24 tracked ESLint complexity suppressions (137 -> 113) across extension dispatch/policy/tool-schema, MCP server dispatch, bootstrap/list/registration helpers, core item-format, linked-test parser/assertions, search filters/scorer, and calendar range/filter helpers. Focused regression passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extensions/extension-command.spec.ts tests/unit/cli/main-loose-options.spec.ts tests/unit/core/extensions/extension-policy.spec.ts tests/unit/extensions/runtime-registrations.spec.ts tests/unit/sdk/action-schema-parity.spec.ts tests/unit/sdk/sdk-index.spec.ts tests/unit/core/item-format.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/search.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/calendar.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/test-command.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts (8 files, 357 tests passed)."
  "2026-06-30T22:05:08.996Z",claude-code-agent,"Manual test evidence: strict temp-dir smoke passed with sandboxed PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH. Covered init, create with deadline, files link, linked test add/run with JSON assertion, list/search, install calendar + calendar JSON output, package init/install, generated package command, and package doctor deep. Smoke item: pm-l2gw in temporary tracker; temp directory removed."
  "2026-06-30T22:30:03.222Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence update: complexity baseline now drops from 146 to 113 individual ESLint complexity suppressions versus main (33 removed). The PR removes 9 suppressed file entries entirely and cuts the largest MCP dispatcher from a 100+ complexity-point hotspot into handler primitives. Verification passed: pnpm typecheck; focused suites 122 tests; full coverage 262 files / 5260 tests at 100/100/100/100; pnpm lint; pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:docs-links; pnpm security:scan; pnpm audit --audit-level low; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog 2026.6.30 and unchanged CHANGELOG.md; Sentry/telemetry gate ok with 0 critical/high Sentry issues and telemetry finish_error_rate_pct 0.77; release:gates passed through build/typecheck/docs/static/full coverage/version/security/npx smoke/package-first dogfood and stopped only at Greptile because changes were not committed yet. Greptile will be rerun after commit and before push."
  "2026-06-30T22:36:54.977Z",claude-code-agent,"Greptile pre-push review evidence: greptile review --branch main --agent completed as review 21a5b4f0-110a-4cda-9dfa-a7f808ebe33b with Confidence 5/5 and no review comments. Summary confirmed extension/MCP dispatch tables and extracted item-format/policy helpers preserve behavior."
